title: Triend Zoned 2/26: Maria Sharapova, Face Masks, Little Caesar’s, Jobs for Miserable People
itunes:title: Triend Zoned 2/26: Maria Sharapova, Face Masks, Little Caesar’s, Jobs for Miserable People
description:
On this edition of Triend Zoned Jack and Miles discuss Maria Sharapova retiring, a Texas manufacturer can’t meet the demand for face masks in the wake of Corona Virus, Little Caesar’s is doing a campaign with a cardboard thrown, and the boys discuss miserable jobs trending on twitter as well as their own.
